<module>
    <h>sgìth</h>
    <p><g>sgìth</g> <adj/>
        <en>tired</en></p>

<section>
    <h>nouns</h>
    <module id="duine">
        <h>duine</h>
        <p><g><a href="?gd=duine">duine</a> sgìth</g>
            <en>a tired man</en> – <xl>
                <li>
                    <gd>Tha an duine sin sgìth.</gd>
                    <tr>That man is tired.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 79</ref>
                </li>
            </xl>
        </p>
    </module>
</section>
    
    <section>
        <h>verbs</h>
        <module id="obair">
            <h>obair</h>
            <p><g>sgìth [ag] <a href="?gd=obair">obair</a></g>
                <en>tired working</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri sgìth. Tha i sgìth ag obair anns an
                            achadh.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary is tired. She is tired working in the field.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 7</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Seumas sgìth: tha e ag obair gu trang anns an achadh.</gd>
                        <tr>James is tired: he is working busily in the field.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 7 [adapted]</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha mi sgìth le obair.</gd>
                        <tr>I am tired with work.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 244</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
    </section>
    
    <section id="other">
        <h>other</h>
        <p>
            <xl>
                <li>
                    <gd>Bha Màiri agus Seumas anns a’ mhonadh an dé. [...] Bha iad glé sgìth nuair a thàinig iad dhachaidh feasgar.</gd>
                    <tr>Mary and James were on the moor yesterday. [...] They were very tired when they came home in the evening.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 76</ref>
                </li>
            </xl>
        </p>
    </section>
    
    

</module>
